# 🐍 Python Assignments – SV

![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8%2B-blue.svg)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-active-brightgreen)
![License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/Sadanki/python_assignments_SV)

## 📘 Project Description

This repository contains a series of Python-based assignments focusing on practical scripting skills useful for system administration, DevOps automation, and security checks. Each assignment is structured to help you build confidence with real-world coding scenarios.

---

## 📁 Folder Structure

```
python_assignments_SV/
├── Q1_password_strength.py
├── Q2_cpu_monitor.py
├── Q3_config_parser.py
├── Q4_backup_script.py
├── requirements.txt
├── README.md
└── config/
    └── sample_config.ini
```

